{"tid":2104354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝我公司兩個港豬師奶主動話要去投票⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-07-12T01:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T02:18:42.000Z","uid":36494,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e91987bb18e7d75eae96bf6f5592ee203acb8bd4","tid":2104354,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"公司有幾件港豬型師奶<br />\n今次初選我都廢事嘥口水同佢哋解釋乜嘢事，無叫過佢哋去投<br />\n<br />\n今朝返到公司（星期日仲要開工可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n居然聽到兩個港豬師奶同事，話收工要去投票<br />\n隱約聽到佢地話趁有得投好投驚未來無得投，驚俾公安捉去中國，又話尋日見好多人排隊<br />\n<br />\n聽佢哋對答聽得出佢哋唔明初選目的係乜嘢，但因為對中共的恐懼，加上見尋日全港好多人排隊去投，所以都驅使佢哋出嚟投"},{"pid":"dc9cd33fd2eb285d32b372f00925acd6f48cda90","tid":2104354,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"利申：尋日投咗，而家仲係公司"},{"pid":"d7785fac8565cfe005bb33b484106635444ca570","tid":2104354,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"搵票站同 Code：<a href=\"https://legco2020.com/news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2Fnews&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=6050473c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/news</a><br />\n參選名單同候選人資料：<a href=\"https://legco2020.com/candidates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2Fcandidates&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=36314d0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/candidates</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjV9c6g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjV9c6g.png&h=98409905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLbgCxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLbgCxW.png&h=ebdfabd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a8238d6683f94cf5e5333d9ac0bac3a3c66f229","tid":2104354,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re